<div class="media-item__summary size--large is-centered  ">
<header class="summary-header">
<p class="category">
<a href="https://www.politico.com/news/foreign-policy" target="_blank">foreign policy</a></p>
</header>
<h2 class="headline">Trump bet on Kim. Now he’s disappeared.</h2>
<p class="dek">With North Korea's paramount leader gone missing, the president's personal diplomacy now seems even more fruitless.</p>
</div>
